mods.abstract: Two color window card (black on yellow) announcing Grand Ole Opry stars Wilma Lee and Stoney Cooper and band with Stringbean, Marti Brown, Merle Kilgore, and Ernie Ashworth at Fonner Park on July 25 and 26. The poster features a metal photoplate of Wilma Lee, Stoney Cooper, Stringbean, Marti Brown, Merle Kilgore, and Ernie Ashworth.
